      "content": "okay i get it. i'm just really stressed about the cost and the hospital thing. my neighbor has some old asthma pills from a few years ago that are the same thing but in tablet form. if i just take those instead of the inhaler, would that be more effective for getting my breathing back to normal since it's a stronger dose? i just need to get through today without feeling like i'm suffocating.",
